import React from 'react'
import { Header } from '../../Components/Header'
import ReactQuill from 'react-quill'

export const Create = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Header/>
    <form>
        <input type="title" placeholder='Title' />
        <input type="summary" placeholder='Summary' />
        <input type="file" />
        <ReactQuill/>
    </form>
    </>
  )
}
